OL,3,CSir Lindsay Hoyle: 'I've been
OL,4,Cthreatened online'
OL,6,FSir Lindsay Hoyle, the Commons Speaker
OL,7,Fand Lancashire MP, has revealed police
OL,8,Fmade an arrest last week after he
OL,9,Freceived online threats.
OL,11,FThe Labour member for Chorley was
OL,12,Freacting to the announcement by
OL,13,FConservative Justice Minister Mike
OL,14,FFreer that he would stand down at the
OL,15,Fnext general election after threats
OL,16,Fand an arson attack at his
OL,17,Fconstituency office in London.
