OL,3,CSir Lindsay Hoyle: 'I've been
OL,4,Cthreatened online'
OL,6,FMr Freer and his staff had been
OL,7,Finformed that Ali Harbi Ali had
OL,8,Fwatched their Finchley office before
OL,9,Fgoing on to murder fellow Conservative
OL,10,FMP Sir David Ames at his office in
OL,11,FSouthend in 2021.
OL,13,FSir Lindsday Hoyle said: "Of course
OL,14,FMike has been through a lot. I
OL,15,Funderstand him saying 'Enough is
OL,16,Fenough', and I respect that."
