OL,3,CSir Lindsay Hoyle: 'I've been
OL,4,Cthreatened online'
OL,6,FHe said he had been threatened in
OL,7,Fposts online on Friday 26 January: "I
OL,8,Ffaced threats as well and the police
OL,9,Fhad to make an arrest on the basis of
OL,10,Fthreats that are coming in all the
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,F"I got lots of that and it shouldn't
OL,14,Fgo with the job but unfortunately it
OL,15,Fdoes come with the job."
OL,17,FHe said the abuse related to his work
OL,18,Fas the Chorley MP, but didn't go
OL,19,Ffurther as to their nature.
